{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"platforms":[{"name":"Brunow","introducedAt":"2017.01.20"}],"title":"Everyone Is Shouting"},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If everyone is shouting then joining them only adds to the noise. The first person to shout gets a reward but each person after her gets less. It doesn’t add to impact or success but instead makes the world a little bit worse. It drives away anyone who is following closely — those who truly care about what you’re doing.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/06-02-everyone-is-shouting","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/06-02-everyone-is-shouting"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-06-02T23:40:30-05:00"}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","title":"2016","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"type":"topic"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","title":"Archive","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","abstract":[{"text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have somethin